claim.claim-text:
A linear compressor (100), comprising:
a shell (101) comprising a suction inlet (104);
a cylinder (120) provided in the shell (101) to define a compression space for a refrigerant;
a piston (130) reciprocated in an axial direction within the cylinder (120);
a discharge valve (161) provided at one end of the cylinder (120) to selectively discharge the refrigerant compressed in the compression space;
at least one nozzle (122) disposed on the cylinder (120) and through which at least a portion of the refrigerant discharged through the discharge valve (161) flows; and
at least one expansion portion (200) that extends from the at least one nozzle (122) to an inner circumferential surface of the cylinder (120), wherein the expansion portion (200) has a cross-sectional area greater than a cross-sectional area of the at least one nozzle (122).
